org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.core.dom

Class DefaultASTVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.core.dom.ASTVisitor
      • org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.core.dom.DefaultASTVisitor

  • public class DefaultASTVisitor
extends ASTVisitor
    An ASTVisitor that can be configured to have a default implementation for all nodes. Provisional API: This class/interface is part of an interim API that is still under development and expected to change significantly before reaching stability. It is being made available at this early stage to solicit feedback from pioneering adopters on the understanding that any code that uses this API will almost certainly be broken (repeatedly) as the API evolves.
